Description: Calculates daily climate water balance for irrigation purposes. 
    The package also calculates the reference or potential evapotranspiration using three methods.
    Penman and Monteith, Priestley and Taylor, and Hargreaves and Samani. 
    It also allows the use of crop and water stress coefficients.
